---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Alex Wilson" description="Alex Wilson writes about the things he's trying to understand.">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p class="intro__text">
      This is the website of Alex Wilson. Here you will find my musings about the world, mostly intended for myself, but some of which others may find interesting.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="post__content">
    <p>
      I like things with discoverable depth: surfaces that reward curiosity, experiences that reveal themselves slowly. Games that teach you to break them. Conversations that wander somewhere unexpected.
    </p>

    <h2>Beliefs</h2>
    <i class="section-subtitle">Some strongly held, some loosely held.</i>
    <p>
    I believe in play.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in seeking slack.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in looking at things with enchanted eyes — choosing to see wonder, choosing to be delighted.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in the seasons. There are seasons of growth, seasons of decay, seasons of quiet frost, seasons of bountiful joy and harvest. Friendships have seasons. Careers have seasons. Selves have seasons.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in sleeping in.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in food that makes your soul sing.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in the importance of friendship.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in laughter and in serious thought.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in interpretting words and actions charitably.
    </p>
    </ul>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/awlego" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/awlego" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <footer class="about-footer">
    <p>I am not under any NDA or other agreement that would preclude me from revealing that such an agreement exists.</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 + .section-subtitle {
    display: block;
    margin-top: -0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e0e0e0);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #666);
  }

  .about-footer p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
